# Lico Integrated Gitignore

## Dependencies
node_modules/
.venv/

## Temporary files
.trash/
.temp/
*.lock
!uv.lock
!yarn.lock
!.gitkeep

## Project Base
.runtimes/
.repos/

## Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

## IDEs
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/*.code-snippets

## Shared Shadows & Skills
.agent/skills/.shadow/assets/
.agent/skills/licochron-history/assets/
.agent/skills/licoproj/assets/

## Identifiers Workspace
.agent/.internal/workspace/iuria/
